-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

For physics details on the PIRAnha suite of subtraction methods, see:

   [Safe Drop paper]

For physics details on iterated voronoi subtraction and optimal transport subtraction, see:

   The Hidden Geometry of Particle Collisions.
   Patrick T. Komiske, Eric M. Metodiev, Jesse Thaler.
   JHEP 07 (2020) 006, arXiv:2004.04159.

For additional physics details on the energy mover's distance, see:

   The Metric Space of Collider Events.
   Patrick T. Komiske, Eric M. Metodiev, Jesse Thaler.
   Phys. Rev. Lett. 123 (2019) 041801, arXiv:1902.02346.

